com.sap.spe.conversion

Interface IDimension

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public interface IDimension
extends java.io.Serializable
    Represents a dimension such as MASS, VOLUME, LENGTH etc. All physical and all quantity units have a dimension. The physical unit kg i.e have the dimension MASS. Quantity units like PIECE (PC) are related to dimension DIMENSIONLESS
